race.description: Sportsbet Nobody Does It Easier Maiden Plate
race.comment: OTTELIA (12) started at big odds on debut last start when a close fourth over 1200m at Warrnambool. Will be very hard to beat with that run under the belt. ALL TOO TRUE (1) was prominent at the turn first-up at Strathalbyn but just lacked a fitness edge late. Better for the hit-out and has enough pace to offset the draw and be handy again. FINANCE MERCHANT (6) returns for the Purcell camp. Was solid on debut without threatening the winner. Looks to have come on nicely during the break, taking benefit from a Warnambool jump-out. Draws well and can play a role. CAN'TALLBEGEMS (5) should be sharpened by the blinkers after a soft debut effort. Keeping safe.
